reviewText: In answer to a reviewer, "More Than Stretch" video is available in DVD. No longer in VHS to my knowledge. See agelessandmoving dot com

This is a perfect workout for someone(older adults and seniors)  wanting to begin an exercise program involving stretching, toning and balance.  Combines yoga and pilates in a well-paced program which includes some more difficult moves to consider as you progress. You feel good when you finish the program.  Wish it was available in DVD.
